  "texts": [
    "We first tested the models on their high-level visual understanding of the scenes: we tasked them with determining the background colour and the number of blocks in the image.",
    "To test their physical understanding, we tested them on the same task as the original study: we asked them to give a binary rating on the stability of the depicted block towers.",
    "For the first two tasks, we calculated the percentage of correct answers for each of the models.",
    "For the third task, we calculated a Bayesian linear mixed effects regression between human and model answers.",
    "Due to the limited sample size of the original human experiment, we reran the human experiment from ref."
  ],
